## 8. `frontend/src/pages/AnalyzerPage.tsx`

Main page component — orchestrates all components:

```typescript
export function AnalyzerPage() {
  const { submitMutation, statusQuery, reset } = useAnalysis();
  const status = statusQuery.data?.status;

  // State machine:
  // idle → show UploadForm
  // submitting/polling (not terminal) → show ProgressTracker
  // COMPLETED/PARTIAL → show results (ScoreGauge + SalaryRange + ExplanationPanel)
  // FAILED → show error message
  // submit error → show ErrorBanner

  // Page header: 'CV Analyzer' title, subtitle
  // 'Start over' button when in results or failed state
}
```

Layout:
- Max width container (max-w-3xl, centered)
- Clean white/grey background
- Card-style sections for results

